summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department, authorizing the sale and removal of certain alder timber, other hardwoods, cottonwood, and certain salvageable forest materials from City-owned lands in Townships 22 and 23, North, Range 7 East, W.M., Townships 21, 22 and 23 North, Range 8 East, W.M., and Township 22 North, Range 9 East, W.M., in the Cedar River Watershed under contract with Masao Nakaso.
